title: CCK Podcast: Avengers Assemble (with Zah, Brandon Walker, Robbie Fox, Ellie Schnitt, Trent, Marty Mush, Jared Carrabis, Kayce Smith and KFC)
description:
An ensemble cast Zah returning from Zimbabwe, Brandon Walker and Kayce on college football, Robbie Fox catching Jared Carrabis up on nerd culture (and regular human being culture), Trent, Ellie and Marty doing relationship advice and more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
